'''開放網路基金會'''（{{lang-en|Open Networking Foundation}}，縮寫'''ONF'''）是一个[[非营利性|非营利性]]的[[產業聯盟|產業聯盟]]，成員包括[[德国电信|德国电信]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Google|Google]]、[[微軟|微軟]]、[[威訊通信|威訊通信]]和[[雅虎|雅虎]]。其宗旨在於推動[[軟體定義網路|軟體定義網路]]（SDN）和规范[[OpenFlow|OpenFlow]]协议与相关技术，以促進網際網路的進步。<ref>{{cite web |title= Open Networking Foundation Formed to Speed Network Innovation |work= Press release |date= March 21, 2011 |publisher= Open Networking Foundation |url= http://archive.openflow.org/wp/2011/03/open-networking-foundation-formed-to-speed-network-innovation/ |accessdate= October 30, 2016 |archive-date= 2014-01-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140116023421/http://archive.openflow.org/wp/2011/03/open-networking-foundation-formed-to-speed-network-innovation/ |dead-url= yes }}</ref>该标准制定和SDN促进组织将使计算机与网络之间的[[雲端運算|雲端運算]]模糊化。<ref>{{Cite news |author= {{tsl|en|John Markoff}} |work= New York Times |title= Open Networking Foundation Pursues New Standards |date= March 22, 2011 |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/22/technology/internet/22internet.html |accessdate= October 30, 2016 |archive-date= 2021-02-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210225135811/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/03/22/technology/internet/22internet.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>该计划旨在通过电信网络、[[无线网络|无线网络]]、[[数据中心|数据中心]]和其他网络领域中的简单软件更改来加速创新。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.computerworld.com.au/article/380663/google_other_titans_form_open_networking_foundation/?fp=4&fpid=78268965 |title=ComputerWorld: “Google and other titans form Open Networking Foundation.” Noyes, March 23, 2011. |access-date=2017-08-05 |archive-date=2011-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110406121956/http://www.computerworld.com.au/article/380663/google_other_titans_form_open_networking_foundation/?fp=4&fpid=78268965 |dead-url=no }}</ref>  

{{as of|2013|12|31}}，该组织有123个公司成员。{{as of|2014|6}}，开放网络基金会已发展到150多家公司成员，其中包括24家软件定义网络的[[初创公司|初创公司]]。<ref>[http://www.eweek.com/blogs/first-read/sdn-consortium-adds-24-startups-to-its-membership-list.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eweek.com/blogs/first-read/sdn-consortium-adds-24-startups-to-its-membership-list.html |date=20190712235626 }} ''Eweek'',"SDN Consortium Adds 24 Startups to Its Membership List", June 18, 2014.  Retrieved 2014-09-17.</ref>公司成员包括网络设备供应商、[[半导体|半导体]]公司、计算机公司、软件公司、[[互联网服务供应商|电信服务运营商]]、{{tsl|en|hyperscale|超大规模}}数据中心运营商，以及企业用户。

在2016年，ONF宣布<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.opennetworking.org/news-and-events/press-releases/3194-open-networking-foundation-and-on-lab-to-merge-to-accelerate-adoption-of-sdn|title=Open Networking Foundation and ON.Lab to Merge to Accelerate Adoption of SDN - Open Networking Foundation|website=www.opennetworking.org|language=en-gb|access-date=2017-03-31|archive-date=2017-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401143739/https://www.opennetworking.org/news-and-events/press-releases/3194-open-networking-foundation-and-on-lab-to-merge-to-accelerate-adoption-of-sdn|dead-url=yes}}</ref>打算与开放网络实验室（ON.Lab）合并。所产生的实体将保留ONF名称，两个非营利组织的合并预计将在2017年完成。

